title: Truls Vasvik
text:
Truls Vasvik (born 28 June 1978) is a Norwegian politician.
He was elected representative to the <a href="Storting">Storting</a> from the constituency of <a href="Vestfold">Vestfold</a> for the period 2021–2025, for the <a href="Labour%20Party%20%28Norway%29">Labour Party</a>. He was deputy representative to the Storting 2017–2021.
